  <style type="text/css">
   .control { display: inline; font: 1em/1 Ahem, sans-serif; background: red; color: white; }
   .test { border: solid blue; font: 1em/1 Ahem; background: yellow; color: orange; width: 19em; }
   .normal { white-space: normal; }
   .nowrap { white-space: nowrap; }
   .pre { white-space: pre; }
  </style>
 </head>
 <body>
  <div class="control">Ahem_font_required_for_this_test.</div>
  <p>There should be a pretty yellow and orange pattern and the word "PASS" in orange on white below.</p>
